</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://www.eventhelix.com/RealtimeMantra/Networking/bgp_startup.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.eventhelix.com/RealtimeMantra/Networking/bgp_startup.pdf" rel="nofollow">BGP Interactions at Router Startup Described as a Sequence Diagram</a> (PDF)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mudynamics.com/products/protocol.html" class="external text" title="http://www.mudynamics.com/products/protocol.html" rel="nofollow">BGP Protocol Service Level Traffic Variations</a> <a href="/wiki/Mu_Dynamics" title="Mu Dynamics">Mu Dynamics</a></li>
</ul>


